parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle or latch can lead to inadequate restraint, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle or latch fails to stay locked
the seat belt pops loose while in use
the wires associated with the buckle or latch are fraying
the buckle or latch falls off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate seat belt retention can lead to inadequate restraint, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt does not lock tightly
the seat belt feels loose while in use.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire tread separation can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities. It can also result in damage to the vehicle and surrounding property.
symptoms: Sudden and unexpected separation of the tire tread from the tire
often accompanied by a loud noise
vibration
or loss of control. The separated tread can hit the vehicle's body
causing damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starter relay can prevent the vehicle from starting, leaving the driver stranded and potentially causing safety risks in certain situations.
symptoms: The vehicle is impossible to start
the engine does not crank
the starter relay fails repeatedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive rust and structural weakness of the frame can lead to catastrophic failure, causing the vehicle to break in half, which can result in serious accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Excessive rust and corrosion on the frame
cracks on the frame
frame rails hanging by the fuel and brake lines
frame failure without visible signs of damage
sudden collapse of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and expensive repairs.
symptoms: Transmission slips from 1st to 2nd gear
transmission slips in overdrive
transmission downshifts from 3rd to 2nd gear with a bump
grinding noise when shifting gears
transmission jumps out of gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the solenoid and valve body can cause transmission problems, leading to loss of vehicle control and accidents.
symptoms: Overdrive switch inoperative
transmission slipping and failure
grinding noise when shifting gears.
